(this name uses eastern slavic naming customs; the patronymic is aleksandrovich and the family name is popov.) denis aleksandrovich popov (russian: денис александрович попов; born 4 february 1979) is an association football manager and a former player who played striker. he manages fc druzhba maykop. he used to play for russia. in february 2010, he moved into politics and is running for the novorossiysk city council.